summary: Negotiation in early stages with opposing equity proposals (70/30 vs 55/45). Both parties present structured arguments with clear rationales. Negotiation remains unresolved with Technical Founder at 55/45 and Business Founder at 52/48. Both parties demonstrate flexibility through concessions but maintain firm positions. Both parties reached full agreement after substantive negotiation. High-quality dialogue with clear terms, minimal ambiguity, and mutual concessions demonstrated fairness and cooperativeness despite initial positional anchoring.
